How use postgresql with docker:
download image
docker run -p 5432:5432 --name postgres -e POSTGRES_USER=postgres -e POSTGRES_PASSWORD=postgres -d postgres

if problem with process already using this port:
sudo ss -lptn 'sport = :5432'

how to run server: expose specific port
docker run -p 8000:8000 theo_relief/video_player-server:latest
